30-1 Game Dev I

Project Wizard Screen -- Start project
New Folder for Project
Import packages: all unchecked
Setup defaults for 3D, always
CREATE

Concepts:
Scene files - canvas files (canvas for photoshop files), levels
scene tab - 3D camera view for the world
hierarchy tab - list of objects in the scene (not just in the window), including the invisibles
main camera
game objects
inspector tab - displays detailed information on currently selected game object

left click on main camera - highlight

hierarchy tab -> create -> cube

project tab -> file browser -> materials

game tab -> camera == what the player will see

Export == building (compiling/baking)

